  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this WFP project is to provide food assistance services to IDPs in Miabi and Demba. With this CERF grant, WFP will procure and distribute 533 tonnes of food. WFP will also distribute USD1,735,917 in cash transfer. The project will last nine months and will benefit 78,195 people including 12,281 women, 21,599 girls and 782 people living with disabilities.</narrative>
